quran[5{c,v,t}:
2,220,"puchhte hain : yatimon ke sath kya maamla kya jaye? kaho : jis tarz amal mein un ke liye bhalai ho, wohi ikhtiyar karna behtar hai agar tum apna aur unn ka kharch aur rehna sehna mushtarik rakho, to is mein koi muzaiqa nahi aakhir woh tumahray bhai band hi to hain buraiee karne walay aur bhalai karne walay, dono ka haal Allah par roshan hai Allah chahta to is muamlay mein tum par sakhti karta, magar woh sahib ikhtiyar honay ke sath sahib hikmat bhi hai"
2,221,"tum mushriq aurton se hargiz nikah nah karna, jab taq ke woh imaan nah le ayen aik momin londi mushriq shareef zadi se behtar hai, agarchay woh tumhe bohat pasand ho aur apni aurton ke nikah mushriq mardon se kabhi nah karna, jab taq ke woh imaan nah le ayen aik momin ghulam mushriq shareef se behtar hai agarchay woh tumhe bohat pasand ho yeh log tumhe aag ki taraf bulatay hain aur Allah apne azan se tum ko jannat aur mughfirat ki taraf bulaataa hai, aur woh apne ehkaam wazeh tor par logon ke samnay bayan karta hai, tawaqqa hai ke woh sabaq lain ge aur nasihat qubool karen ge"
2,222,"puchhte hain : haiz ka kya hukum hai? kaho : woh aik gandagi ki haalat hai is mein aurton se allag raho aur un ke qareeb nah jao, jab taq ke woh pak saaf nah ho jayen phir jab woh pak ho jayen, to unn ke paas jao uss terhan jaissa ke Allah ne tum ko hukum diya hai Allah unn logon ko pasand karta hai, jo badi se baz rahen aur pakizgee ikhtiyar karen"
2,223,"tumhari aurtain tumhari khityan hain tumhe ikhtiyar hai, jis terhan chaho, apni khaiti mein jao, magar apne mustaqbil ki fikar karo aur Allah ki narazi se bachcho khoob jaan lau ke tumhe aik din uss se milna hai aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! jo tumhari Hadayat ko maan lain inhen Falah o Saadat ka musardah suna do"
2,224,"Allah ke naam ko aisi kasmain khanay ke liye istemaal nah karo, jin se maqsood neki aur taqwa aur bandgaan khuda ki bhalai ke kamon se baz rehna ho Allah tumhari saari baatein sun raha hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
